'''''To Walk with Lions''''' ni film yo mu 1999 iyobowe na Carl Schultz ikinwamo na Richard Harris nka George Adamson na John Michie nka Tony Fitzjohn <ref>BBC - Films - review - To Walk With Lions DVD</ref>. Bikurikiranye imyaka yakurikiyeho Ntare wunganira Adamson<ref>to walk with lions - MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › films › to-walk-with-lions</ref>. Nyuma yo gushyingiranwa na Joy Adamson wa ''Born Free'' fame, Adamson yamaze igice cya nyuma cyubuzima bwe arinda intare n’ibindi binyabuzima muri Kora National Reserve, [[Kenya]] <ref>To Walk With Lions - Where to Watch and Stream - TV Guide <nowiki>https://www.tvguide.com</nowiki> › movies › to-walk-with-lions</ref>. Ahura na ba rushimusi na ruswa ya leta imubuza gushaka kubungabunga inyamaswa<ref>Lion Movie May Help Kenya Film Industry Roar - CSMonitor.com <nowiki>https://www.csmonitor.com</nowiki> › 050598.intl.intl.4.html</ref>.

== Umugambi ==
Tony Fitzjohn (John Michie) aje gukora kuri Kora, kubungabunga intare, kubavandimwe babiri bageze mu zabukuru, George na Terence Adamson ( Ian Bannen )<ref>Review of To Walk With Lions - myReviewer.com <nowiki>https://www.myreviewer.com</nowiki> › Review-by-petergee</ref>. Ku munsi we wa mbere, Fitzjohn yirengagije inama za George zo kutiruka kandi hafi yarakubiswe<ref>To Walk With Lions | Movie Synopsis and info - Tribute.ca <nowiki>https://www.tribute.ca</nowiki> › movies › to-walk-with-lions</ref>. Kumenyeshwa ubu nuburyo umuntu wa nyuma wujuje umwanya we yapfuye<ref>To Walk with Lions (1999) | Radio Times <nowiki>https://www.radiotimes.com</nowiki> › movie-guide › b-boqsqt</ref>, Fitzjohn yanditse ahantu hose nk'umusazi ahitamo kugenda<ref>"To Walk with Lions" Trailer - WildlifeNOW <nowiki>https://wildlifenow.com</nowiki> › to-walk-with-lions-trailer</ref>. Nyuma yumunota wanyuma uhinduye umutima, hamwe n'icyana cy'intare cyamuzanye muri pariki kugirango amutoze kandi yongere yinjire mwishyamba, avumbura umuhamagaro wukuri mubuzima bwe<ref>Top 10 Lion Movies | Asilia Africa <nowiki>https://www.asiliaafrica.com</nowiki> › blog › top-10-lion-movies</ref>.

